OL,3,CAdmin worker unfairly sacked after
OL,4,Caccidentally abusing client, tribunal
OL,5,Crules
OL,7,FNOTE: Article includes language that
OL,8,Fsome may find offensive.
OL,10,FAn admin worker who was sacked after
OL,11,Fcalling a customer an offensive word
OL,12,Fin an email which she accidentally
OL,13,Fsent to them, has won more than #5,000
OL,14,Fin an unfair dismissal claim.
OL,16,FMeliesha Jones, who had been a part-
OL,17,Ftime administrator at Vale Curtains
OL,18,Fand Blinds in Oxford since May 2021,
OL,19,Fwas dealing with a customer complaint
OL,20,Fwith a colleague when she hit the
OL,21,Fwrong button.
