OL,3,CAdmin worker unfairly sacked after
OL,4,Caccidentally abusing client, tribunal
OL,5,Crules
OL,7,FShe wrote: "Hi Karl ` Can you change
OL,8,Fthis... he's a twat so it doesn't
OL,9,Fmatter if you can't."
OL,11,FBy mistake, instead of clicking
OL,12,F"forward" she had clicked "reply", so
OL,13,Fthe email was sent to the customer
OL,14,Finstead of Mr Gibbons.
OL,16,FShortly afterwards the customer's wife
OL,17,Frang up and said "Is there any reason
OL,18,Fwhy you called my husband a twat?"
