OL,5,Crules
OL,7,FShe threatened to go to the press and
OL,8,Fsocial media and Mrs Smith said she
OL,9,Fwould investigate the matter and get
OL,10,Fback to her.
OL,12,FMs Jones said she would offer to pay
OL,13,Fthe customer #500 out of her own
OL,14,Fpocket as "a gesture of goodwill."
OL,16,FThe tribunal heard that an
OL,17,Finvestigation took place and the
OL,18,Fcompany decided there also had to be a
OL,19,Fdisciplinary hearing.
OL,26,@vD@KOUvD@bO]
