OL,3,CAdmin worker unfairly sacked after
OL,4,Caccidentally abusing client, tribunal
OL,5,Crules
OL,7,FEmployment Judge Akua Reindorf KC
OL,8,Fsaid: "I conclude from the evidence
OL,9,Fbefore me that the principal reason
OL,10,Ffor his decision was that the customer
OL,11,Fand his wife had made threats to
OL,12,Fpublicise the Claimant's email in the
OL,13,Fpress, social media and/or Trustpilot."
OL,15,FShe added: "I am satisfied that if a
OL,16,Ffair procedure had been followed,
OL,17,Fthere is no chance that the claimant
OL,18,Fwould have been dismissed.
