OL,7,FShe added that the company had
OL,8,F"decided to sacrifice the claimant's
OL,9,Femployment for the sake of appeasing
OL,10,Fthe customer and heading off bad
OL,11,Freviews, and wholly unreasonably
OL,12,Ffailed to consider other more
OL,13,Fproportionate ways of achieving the
OL,14,Fsame outcome."
OL,16,FShe described Ms Jones's sending of
OL,17,Fthe email as "improper and
OL,18,Fblameworthy" and that she had been
